arker at the world economic forum in  mark parker born  october  is the chief executive officer of nike inc he was named the third ceo of the company in  contents  early life  career at nike  art collection  references early lifeedit parker was born in poughkeepsie new york the son of elizabeth and bruce parker he earned his bachelors degree in political science at penn state university in  he is married to kathy parker and has three children jennifer megan and matthew he ran on the penn state track and cross country teams career at nikeedit parker joined nike in  as a footwear designer based in its rd facility in exeter new hampshire he became division vice president in charge of development in  corporate vice president in  general manager in  and vice president of global footwear in  prior to becoming vice president of nike he served as copresident with charlie denson of the nike brand beginning in march  he still participates in shoe design most notably on the nike htm project creating limited edition footwear alongside nike designer tinker hatfield and creative consultant hiroshi fujiwara he has committed to ensuring that nike remain environmentally conscious after  years of work parker and his team launched the first green shoe that adheres to the principles of sustainability he is also responsible for other brands in nikes portfolio including converse inc and hurley internationalcitation needed while ceo of nike in  mark g parker earned a total compensation of  which included a base salary of  a cash bonus of  stocks granted of  options granted of  and nonequity incentive plan compensation listed at  after being promoted to chairman in  mark parkers compensation tripled to over  million   million of which came from stock rewards in  mark parker was named fortunes businessperson of the year it was announced in june  that mark parker is replacing phil knight as company chairman of nike in   art collectionedit parker is an avid arts supporter with an extensive ongoing collection of modern low brow and underground contemporary art along with many other oneofakind collectiblescitation needed notable artists from parkers collection include andy warhol adonna khare mark ryden todd schorr tim biskup eric white sebastian kruger charles krafft glennray tutor robert crumb chris mars sarina brewer and michael leavittcitation needed other notable items include rare movie ephemera such as original props and models from mars attacks  the day the earth stood still  back to the future  and batman  referencesedit  a b c d nike website biography  executive profilemark g walker businessweek retrieved  march    bustillo migel may   nike looks beyond its swoosh for growth wall street journal p b   nike the spirit machine c retrieved december     cnn feature on nikes green shoe  nike ceo total pay soars wsj retrieved    mark parker fortune retrieved    phil knight takes steps away from nike will leave as board chairman oregonlivecom retrieved    rivera erica  april  crave profile sarina brewer and rogue taxidermy craveonline craveonlinellc retrieved  november    oshea jamie september  inside mark parkers alternate universe juxtapoz magazine p   v t e nike inc corporate directors jill ker conway tim cook phil knight travis knight mark parker orin c smith john thompson phyllis wise subsidiaries converse hurley former cole haan • umbro • bauer hockey assets and products air jordan air melo line air max nike considered nike ctr maestri nike flywire nike free nike mercurial vapor nike shox nike nike blazers nike sb swoosh air force  nike tiempo nike total  nike multiturf nike air yeezy nike ordem miscellaneous list of nike sponsorships nike academy nike sport research lab nike oregon project nike one v t e the walt disney company company timeline retlaw enterprises criticism company officials founders walter elias disney roy oliver disney executives bob iger ceo alan n braverman sevpgc christine mccarthy cfo board of directors susan arnold john s c