urley internationalcitation needed while ceo of nike in  mark g parker earned a total compensation of  which included a base salary of  a cash bonus of  stocks granted of  options granted of  and nonequity incentive plan compensation listed at  after being promoted to chairman in  mark parkers compensation tripled to over  million   million of which came from stock rewards in  mark parker was named fortunes businessperson of the year it was announced in june  that mark parker is replacing phil knight as company chairman of nike in   art collectionedit parker is an avid arts supporter with an extensive ongoing collection of modern low brow and underground contemporary art along with many other oneofakind collectiblescitation needed notable artists from parkers collection include andy warhol adonna khare mark ryden todd schorr tim biskup eric white sebastian kruger charles krafft glennray tutor robert crumb chris mars sarina brewer and michael leavittcitation needed other notable items include rare movie ephemera such as original props and models from mars attacks  the day the earth stood still  back to the future  and batman  referencesedit  a b c d nike website biography  executive profilemark g walker businessweek retrieved  march    bustillo migel may   nike looks beyond its swoosh for growth wall street journal p b   nike the spirit machine c retrieved december     cnn feature on nikes green shoe  nike ceo total pay soars wsj retrieved    mark parker fortune retrieved    phil knight takes steps away from nike will leave as board chairman oregonlivecom retrieved    rivera erica  april  crave profile sarina brewer and rogue taxidermy craveonline craveonlinellc retrieved  november    oshea jamie september  inside mark parkers alternate universe juxtapoz magazine p   v t e nike inc corporate directors jill ker conway tim cook phil knight travis knight mark parker orin c smith john thompson phyllis wise subsidiaries converse hurley former cole haan • umbro • bauer hoc