een a member of the board of directors of nike since  and has been a director of the company since january  mr parker contributes to the mix of experience and qualifications the board seeks to maintain through his experience in various positions at nike through this experience he has gained substantial insights in designing producing and marketing consumer products and in managing major consumer brands sold throughout the world at nike mr parker has also managed a complex global organization and brings to the board his knowledge and skills in financial and executive management executive compensation and management leadership source the walt disney company on    sign up for equilar atlas and view mark g parkers full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like mark g parker more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in mark g parkers network and community follow changes in mark g parkers employment and moneyinmotion connect with mark g parker through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example mark g parker mark g parkers connections  sign up now to view mark g parkers  connections » christine m mccarthy senior executive vice president and chief financial officer the walt disney company jeanne p jackson president product and merchandising nike inc sheryl k sandberg dir and chief operating officer facebook inc thomas e clarke former board member nike inc kevin a mayer senior executive vice president and chief strategy officer the walt disney company alan n braverman senior executive vice president general counsel and secretary the walt disney company robert w matschullat lead director the clorox company maria e lagomasino board member the cocacola company elizabeth j comstock vice chairman chief executive officer business innovations general electric company eric d sprunk chief operating officer nike inc popular profiles 